data.description: Welcome to your home at the Lake! This adorable 3 bedroom 2 bathroom modular home is conveniently located on the Southern shore of Canyon Lake with easy access to New Braunfels, San Antonio, and all that the surrounding area has to offer. Just 1.5 miles from Cranes Mill Park and Marina and only 2.5 miles from the nearest boat ramp, you can live everyday like you're on vacation! Move in ready with brand new carpet in all bedrooms.  Cute and comfy and ready to enjoy. Master bathroom has a big garden tub, separate shower, and double vanity. Enjoy the privacy of the very spacious, fenced in back yard while you sit at the patio and relax. Plenty of storage in the shed and extra parking for your boat, RV, and other toys. Within 10 miles from tubing and concerts on the Guadalupe River and close proximity to great restaurants, wineries and more! There's so much to do in this part of the Texas Hill Country! Don't hesitate to make this your permanent home or weekend retreat at the lake today!!
